Is there any context in which you'd be open to sharing personal feelings, ideas, struggles, etc. in a less abstract way so I could get a better idea of where your art is coming from?

3.20.20  3:00 am   Will you change the framerate to 60fps for the new videos?

     that has been the plan. but i am discovering that 60fps actually exposes the true nature of movement in a way that can be uncomfortable unless you have movement schemes that are no less than gifted. in other words it significantly raises the bar for quality of movement. it also reminds me how blessed it can be to switch and play with different rates within 1 video, which 60 actually can allow nicely

      Thanks and good luck
